title: EUW Team Looking for Jungler and Toplaner p4+ to build up a new team
body:
Hi my name is Londlanor im from EUW, high platinum Elo currently
Im looking forward to build up a new team since teamranked has started again, currently we need a Toplaner and a Jungler.
The goal is at least Diamond 5 in Teamranking and to participate in minor Tournaments.
You should bring with you:
-fluent English(or at least a basic communication ability in English)
-a Soloq rank which should be at least Platinum 4 or above
-Teamspeak or Skype(or both^^)
-the will to build up a new team and the ability to take critism or give constructive critism

If ur Interested just add "Londlanor"
